  "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\nUnable to connect Nimbus Eth2 Client with Nethermind using the WebSockets connection. Works with Geth client.\r\n\r\n**To Reproduce**\r\nSteps to reproduce the behavior:\r\n1. Run Nethermind with the following flags: \r\n```\r\n--Init.WebSocketsEnabled true --JsonRpc.Enabled true --JsonRpc.Host 0.0.0.0\r\n```\r\n2. Download and unpack [nimbus](https://github.com/status-im/nimbus-eth2/releases) \r\n3. Test with `./build/nimbus_beacon_node web3 test ws://localhost:8545`\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\nExpected output from the test command: \r\n```\r\nNetwork: 1\r\nLatest block: 12875484\r\nDeposit root: 0xc56c58848cc548c9afdf4c8658d8105a51249f952e1866de66747c05e8de7098\r\n```\r\n**Actual behaviour**\r\n```\r\nFAT 2021-07-22 09:59:01.641+00:00 Failed to connect to web3 provider         topics=\"eth1\" tid=397493 file=eth1_monitor.nim:1171 err=\"WebSocket connection error: 200 OK\"\r\n```\r\n\r\n**Desktop (please complete the following information):**\r\n - OS: Ubuntu\r\n - Version 21.04\r\n",
